snippet.title: Reptilian Rebellion - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
Originally released on the Wii U eShop, Reptilian Rebellion is a simple but challenging game, you have to kill as many reptilians as you can, keeping an eye on your ammunition, and looking for powerups and friends.
Be also careful with the road, and with the chem trails in the sky.
How many reptilians can you kill?

Reptilian Rebellion (C) Herrero Games
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/461760/Reptilian_Rebellion/
